    • createTargetInsertSparql

      public String createTargetInsertSparql(PatternMatch instance, List<NewEntity> newEntities)
      Creates a SPARQL INSERT query to insert data corresponding to the specified pattern match into the target ontology.

      The target triples are used to generate the query, being populated by the specified pattern match.

      Parameters:
      instance - Data to insert
      newEntities - List of new entities to create
      Returns:
      SPARQL INSERT query

    • createTargetDeleteSparql

      public String createTargetDeleteSparql(PatternMatch instance)
      Creates a SPARQL DELETE query to delete data corresponding to the specified pattern match from the target ontology.
      Parameters:
      instance - Pattern instance to delete
      Returns:
      SPARQL DELETE query, null if the specified instance is based on a blank node
